    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously cared for and preserved. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all maintenance records up to date and no signs of wear. It drives like a dream and offers all the luxury and performance features in peak working order. This is a rare find for a collector or a buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 49000.0,
